          From our first phygital drops to a permanent mint protocol ‚Äî here's where EtchNFT is headed.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {roadmap.map(({ quarter, icon, items }, index) => (
          <div
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#311524] via-[#1B1A34] to-[#123738] text-white/90 p-8 rounded-2xl backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 shadow-xl fade-up"
            style={`animation-delay: ${100 + index * 100}ms; animation-fill-mode: both; animation-name: fadeUp; animation-duration: 0.6s; animation-timing-function: ease-out;`}
          >
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#DB2777] mb-4 text-center">
              {icon} {quarter}
            </h3>
            <ul class="text-center text-gray-300 space-y-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              {items.map((item, i) => (
                <li key={i}>‚Ä¢ {item}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
